                    Capillus laser therapy uses energy in the form of photons pointed at the scalp to stimulate dormant or unhealthy hair follicles by increasing the hair shafts’ diameter. LLLT helps boost the supply of oxygen and nutrients to the hair follicles so that natural regrowth of thicker hair is fueled. Patients can wear the Capillus laser cap for half an hour every other day or 6 minutes each day to reach hair regrowth.
                    <br><br>
                    It’s important to have realistic expectations since the results can vary from patient to patient and they may not be immediate or permanent without consistency. The earlier you start this hair treatment, the more chances of success. Some patients may need to wait for 3 to 6 months of continuous use before seeing any significant hair regrowth.
                </p>
