                    Unlike other forms of LLLT, the Capillus laser cap is quite safe and effective. This device provides full and reliable exposure during treatment. It’s pain-free, non-evasive, and hands-free so you don’t even need to comb your hair. It doesn’t require going under the knife, and you don’t have to take any medications whether topical or oral.
                </p>
            </div>
